  <info>survos/meili-bundle installed.</info>

  Set your Meilisearch credentials in <comment>.env.local</comment>:
    MEILI_SERVER=http://127.0.0.1:7700
    MEILI_ADMIN_KEY=your-admin-key
    MEILI_SEARCH_KEY=your-search-key

  Run migrations to create the index tracking table:
    <comment>symfony console doctrine:schema:update --force</comment>

  Then open the listing:
    <comment>symfony open:local --path={{ open }}</comment>
